The company is invloved in the exploration, development, and production of
natural gas and oil resources in the Rocky Mountain and Mid-Continent/Gulf
States. They own and operate approximately 3,700 miles of transmission,
gathering, and storage lines, as well as own, lease, and operates 33 compressor
